<p>
  These pages exercise every error path in the rendering pipeline &mdash; both
  non-streaming (<code>react_component</code>) and streaming (<code>stream_react_component</code>)
  &mdash; to verify correct error propagation behavior: what shows in the browser,
  what appears in node-renderer logs, and whether Rails raises or swallows the error.
